text: Kartmazovo is a rural locality (a (selo) in Andreyevskoye Rural Settlement, Sudogodsky District of Vladimir Oblast, Russia. Population: == Geography == The village is located 22 km north-east from Sudogda. ==References== Category:Rural localities in Yuryev-Polsky District Category:Sudogodsky Uyezd
title: Kartmazovo, Vladimir Oblast
